    "date": "2022-02-18T14:36:48Z",
    "text": "Protecting Apprenticeship Training for Veterans Act\n\nThis bill adjusts the administration of certain benefits for veterans participating in an apprenticeship or other on-job training during the period between March 1, 2020, and December 21, 2021, including by proportionately reducing the 120-hour monthly training requirement to reflect an individual's period of unemployment without a reduction in training assistance."
